<div data-label="Row" id="r-1597419387866" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1597419387866"><div class="gf_col-lg-12 gf_column" id="c-1597419387779" data-id="1597419387779"><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1597419396404" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1597419396404"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1>CRM / E-Mail Marketing Manager DACH (f/m/d)</h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1597419505905" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1597419505905"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left" data-gemlang="en"><div class="page" title="Page 1"><div class="section" style="background-color: rgb(100.000000%, 100.000000%, 100.000000%)"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'">At </span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Gautami'">​</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Arial'; font-weight: 700">gitti </span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Gautami'">​</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'">we revolutionize the beauty industry with new, innovative, vegan beauty products.We reunite two concepts that the traditional beauty industry seems to have opposed in the last years: <b>beauty from inside and out.</b> What does this mean for us? We strive for a dual power of beauty and mindfulness: we make beauty sustainable by caring for ourselves and our planet. We want to wake this industry up and offer better alternatives, because you and our planet deserve better. We know we can't do this alone. Changing a mindset requires true heroes who consciously live beauty every day and lead the way.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'">gitti is a dynamic start-up based in Berlin with a highly passionate team. We are now looking for a </span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Gautami'">​</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Arial'; font-weight: 700">CRM / E-Mail Marketing Manager DACH (m/f/x).</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'"><b><br></b></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'"><b>Deine Aufgaben</b></span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Verantwortung der operativen Umsetzung von CRM-Kampagnen, automatisierten&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">Life-Cycle-Programmen sowie der transaktionalen E-Mail-Kommunikation</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Konzeption, Entwicklung und Implementierung von Strategien zur Verbesserung von&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">personalisierter Customer Retention &amp; Loyalty</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Ableitung von Maßnahmen für Bestandskundenmarketing basierend auf Kohorten-&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">und CLV Analysen</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Enge Abstimmung mit internen Teams (Online Marketing, Customer Service, Produktm</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">anagement) zur Planung von Email Marketing-Aktivitäten</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Fortlaufende Evaluierung, Überwachung und Reporting von KPI-Entwicklungen</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;"><b>Dein Profil</b></span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;min. drei Jahre Berufserfahrung im Bereich E-Mail-Marketing/CRM im digitalen&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">Umfeld</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Erfolgreich abgeschlossenes Studium der Betriebswirtschaft mit Schwerpunkt&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">Marketing oder ähnlichem</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Umfangreiche Kenntnisse über CLR, CLV und anderen relevanten CRM KPI</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Ausgeprägte, analytische und kommunikative Fähigkeiten, sowie konzeptionelles&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">Denken und organisiertes Arbeiten</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Hohe Einsatzbereitschaft, Eigenverantwortlichkeit und Belastbarkeit</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Innovatives und praxisorientiertes Mindset gepaart mit Pragmatismus und der&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">Fähigkeit hands-on Dinge anzugehen</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Deutsch auf Muttersprachenniveau und fließende Englischkenntnisse</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Erfahrung in der Arbeit mit Emarsys oder ähnlichen CRM Tools ist ein Plus</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;"><b>Deine Benefits</b></span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Du revolutionierst mit uns die Beauty Industrie: mit besseren Produkten für unseren&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">Kunden*innen und unseren Planeten</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Eine unbefristete Anstellung in einem internationalen, schnell wachsenden D2C&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">Beauty Start-ups mit flachen Hierarchien und kurzen Entscheidungswegen</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Den Freiraum, den Beauty Markt und das Unternehmen aktiv mitzugestalten und die&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">Möglichkeit, sich so professionell weiterzuentwickeln</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Du bist Teil einer Kultur des Vertrauens und des Empowerments mit einer positiven&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">und inspirierenden Arbeitsatmosphäre</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;Ein attraktives Gehaltspaket und tolle Karrieremöglichkeiten</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;"><br></span></p></div></div></div></div><p></p><div class="page" title="Page 2"><div class="section"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'">Sounds like a fit? Please send your CV, salary expectations and your earliest possible starting date to <b>jobs@gitti.de</b>. The beauty industry is changing fast, support us to re-inventit. We can't wait to meet you!</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 9.000000pt; font-family: 'Arial'; font-style: italic">“variety is the spice of life” — and a celebrated component of our culture. At gitti, we strive to create an inclusive environment that empowers our employees. We believe that our products benefit from our diverse backgrounds and experiences and are proud to be an equal opportunity employer: all qualified applicants are considered for positions regardless of race, ethnic origin, gender, age, religion or belief, marital status, gender identification, sexual orientation, or disability.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1597419392451" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1597419392451"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm--lg gf-elm--md gf-elm--sm gf-elm--xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><br></p></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit-->
